            <h3 class="text-dark text-lg font-bold mb-3 mt-6">9.3. Escalation Matrix and Regulatory Recourse</h3>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3">Our objective is to resolve all privacy matters internally through our dedicated compliance architecture. However, if your grievance is not resolved to your satisfaction, or if you believe our processing of your personal information violates applicable data-protection laws, you retain the right to escalate the matter.</p>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed mb-3">Depending on your jurisdiction of residence or engagement, you may lodge a formal complaint with the relevant national or regional data-protection supervisory authority.</p>
            <p class="text-foreground leading-relaxed">We will fully cooperate with any legitimate regulatory body or authorised judicial institution in the resolution of escalated disputes.</p>
